/*
The For loop / Java / Oct 10 2019
gbaylis
The for loop, prints a sentence, increments the # of cups by 1 and prints the Integer
The for loop will stop at Cups of coffee this week: 4 (because i < 5)
*/
// I named this program Main, you can name it anything you like
public class Main {
    // boiler plate code
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        
    // start counting at 0 , run the code until less then 5 and increment by 1    
        for(int i=0; i < 5; i++) {
            System.out.println("Cups of coffee this week: " + i);
        }
        
    } 
}

